expression = re.compile(rfc._RFC850_DATETIME_REGEX)
bad_examples = ['Mon Jan  3 03:21:45 2045', 'Thu Oct 31 20:34:22 1982',
    'Monday, 31-Oct-82 03:21:45', 'Monday 31-Oct-82 03:21:45 GMT',
    'Mon, 31 Oct 1982 03:21:45 GMT', 'Thu, 01 Feb 2045 20:34:22 GMT',
    'Something else']
for bad_example in bad_examples:
    self.assertFalse(bool(expression.fullmatch(bad_example)), msg=
        "Bad rfc850 datetime '{d}' matched regex".format(d=bad_example))
